
** MAKE **

make release create an executable without the demos
make demo create an executable  with all the demos inside

** COMMAND LINE **

the syntax is
  ./test.elf -D WORKING_DIRECTORY -P SCRIP_FILE IMAGE
All the debug file will have the following name :
  (WORKING_DIRECTORY)/debug_(IMAGE)
if you are trying to process all the file of a directory like
    ./test.elf -D . -P SCRIP_FILE pbm/*.pbm
the debug files will be stored into debug_pbm/ .
The directory must exist.